lead_paragraph: Jamaican Olympic relay gold medalist Nesta Carter's "B" sample for the use of a banned stimulant at the 2008 Beijing Games has returned positive, two sources familiar with the case told Reuters on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Jamaican Sprinter Carter's 'B' Sample Tests Positive
